<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>9453</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19476</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>贾森正在玩儿电子游戏。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19476</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23250</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这时，有人拍了拍他的肩膀。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23250</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26929</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“贾森。” 雪莉老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26929</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31383</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我说过在儿童中心不能玩儿电子游戏……”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31383</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37021</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对不起，雪莉老师。” 贾森小声回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37021</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40817</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看到自己被大白鲨吃掉了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40817</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46427</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“大家带塑料垃圾袋和报纸来了吗？” 雪莉老师问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>46427</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52685</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“带了。但这些是拿来做什么的呢？” 尼娜很好奇。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52685</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59610</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是一个秘密。” 雪莉老师说。她的双眼放光。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59610</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67243</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“请大家从桌子上拿两只彩笔和一把尺子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67244</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72126</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>放到袋子里，跟我出去吧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72126</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77415</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师带着学生们来到野餐桌旁。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77415</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80657</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有这些野餐桌很好。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80657</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89156</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，如果我们想坐在那棵树下，或者坐在没有野餐桌的公园里呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89156</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92031</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孩子们看着她。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92031</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>97187</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“地是湿的。” 雪莉老师暗示他们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>97187</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101164</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们就会变湿。” 波比说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101164</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105368</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们需要垫子！” 莉琪马上回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105368</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110454</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对！我们需要坐垫！” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110454</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113907</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今天我们就要制作坐垫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113907</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119868</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>除了报纸，把袋子里的所有东西都拿出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119868</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125413</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>首先，我们要把垃圾袋剪小一点。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125413</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129619</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“让报纸滑到袋子底部。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129619</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138705</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>从报纸边缘开始量十厘米，然后剪下多余的部分。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138705</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142997</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师给每个人分剪刀。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142997</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148919</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“量一量。” 波比说。他把尺子放在袋子上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148919</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152755</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“剪下来。” 尼娜剪短袋子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152755</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156989</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好了！” 莉琪拿起袋子说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156989</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162488</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在像包礼物一样把开口折起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162488</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169105</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后用胶带粘上。小心，胶带很黏的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169105</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174285</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>贾森双臂交叉，看上去很不开心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178415</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“贾森，你怎么了？” 雪莉老师问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178415</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182617</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不喜欢做这个手工。” 他生气地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182617</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187125</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“为什么呢？” 雪莉老师皱了皱眉头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187124</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190609</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我妈妈给了我一个粉红色的垃圾袋！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190609</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195672</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我讨厌粉红色！” 贾森把袋子推开。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195672</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202625</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，贾森。粉红色也很好呀。但是如果你想换一个……</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202625</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207659</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>让我想想……有人想和贾森换袋子吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207659</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213510</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我！” 莉琪跳了起来，“我喜欢粉红色！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213510</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219182</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢你，莉琪。你的袋子是什么颜色的？” 雪莉老师问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219182</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223807</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“灰色。可以吗？” 莉琪看着贾森。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223807</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229203</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“灰色是我最喜欢的颜色。” 贾森咧嘴笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229203</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>238330</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“问题解决了。现在我们要在坐垫上画画了！” 雪莉老师对孩子们说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>238330</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241513</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“用彩笔装饰你的坐垫吧！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241523</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>250750</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一定要写上你的名字。这样就完成了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>250750</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>257630</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哇，贾森。你做得太酷了。” 莉琪说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>257630</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>262773</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>贾森在他的坐垫上画了一只大白鲨。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>262773</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>265976</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢。好像还可以。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>265976</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>277749</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如果是画在粉红色的袋子上就很奇怪了！” 他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>